skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my rainfall
des:
Rainfall Screensaver on your Echo Show or Echo Spot device (required a screen). Rainfall Screensaver skill gives a breathtaking audiovisual experience of rainfall with sounds on your Echo Show or Echo Spot. Great fun for your living room, kitchen or bedroom!

+ Ask "Alexa, open My Rainfall" to open skill. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
